 "remarks": "Welcome to 36 Richmond Drive! Tucked into a great Darien neighborhood, this three-bedroom, two-bath ranch is close to everything, bike to Cherry Lawn Park, walk to local shops and restaurants, or hop on the train in minutes. The home sits on a level, corner lot of over half an acre, with stone patios, a built-in grill, and plenty of yard space for play and entertaining. Inside, you&apos;ll find a lower level that&apos;s perfect for hanging out, with a playroom, bar, and a cozy wood-burning stove. Whether you&apos;re ready to update and make it your own, or you&apos;re looking for a project with great potential, this home is a terrific opportunity. All in the award-winning Ox Ridge Blue Ribbon School district!",
